🎉 Join us for an unforgettable evening of elegance and entertainment at Uchi Japanese Gastro and Bar in Phuket! 
-
📅 Save the Date: October 6th
-
Get ready for a night of enchantment at our GEISHA Night II ! 🎎✨

-
Reserve your table now and immerse yourself in the world of Geishas at Uchi! 🌸✨
